**Description:** This rule defines how the public student list page works, allowing users to view and filter students who have published their LIA profiles.

```
# LIA Student Listing Rules

## URL
- `/lia-students`

## Functionality
- Public list of students who published their LIA profiles.
- Filters:
  - Program category
  - School
  - City
  - Term
  - Keyword search (position/title)

## Display
- Uses grid or list view of `<StudentCard>`.
- Each card shows name, position title, school, and program.

## Security
- Only published profiles are shown.
- No private data (email, phone) is revealed unless explicitly permitted.
```
